x}<\/style><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Choose Us<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b3b327 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9b3b327\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">We are looking for conscientious and motivated employees with a positive attitude and strong work ethic<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d448017 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d448017\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.15.0 - 20-08-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>All employees must pass a 90 day probationary period, after which they become eligible for benefits. Benefits include health insurance, vacation and sick time, holidays and other benefits specific to particular positions such as vehicle and cell phone allowance. Applicants must pass criminal background checks and drug and alcohol screening.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a94010 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1a94010\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About Homesafe Company<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-49757f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"49757f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We are leading provider of electronic security and systems integration in Pittsburgh and the tri-state area. We are proud to be a second generation, family-owned business, providing value and stellar service to our customers for over 15 years.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-49ff170 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"49ff170\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The Following Positions Are Currently Available:<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-922954c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"922954c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Fire Alarm Technician<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1464abf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1464abf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We are seeking a highly skilled fire alarm services person to inspect and repair fire alarms in commercial buildings. This is a full time position and requires a valid PA driver\u2019s license, 3-5 years previous experience with certification a plus. We offer company vehicle, cell phone allowance, health insurance, paid vacation, holidays, and sick time (following probationary period). Salary based on experience.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c6e747 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1c6e747\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Burglar Alarm Technician<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d11f667 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d11f667\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We are seeking experienced security technician for our residential and commercial installation department. This is a full time position and requires a valid PA driver\u2019s license, 3-5 years experience in wireless and hard-wired security alarms. Experience in CCTV and\/or access control a plus. We offer company vehicle, cell phone allowance, health insurance, paid vacation, holidays, and sick time (following probationary period). Salary based on experience.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9740a9b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9740a9b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Account Executive<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-77349a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"77349a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Account Executives are responsible for the sale of residential and commercial security solutions. We are seeking proven consultative sales people with excellent communication skills to develop, maintain and build lasting relationships with our customers. Applicants must be self-starters with the ability to do cold calls and successfully close deals. Requires a valid PA driver\u2019s license, successful experience in outside sales, experience in the security industry is a plus.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3dc8c7a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3dc8c7a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Central Station Operators - Emergency Response<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-85441d1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"85441d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">We are seeking responsible, dependable individuals to respond to alarm calls and provide important, lifesaving help.<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5b68d5f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5b68d5f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Account Executive<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element eleme